<p>The <code>switch</code> tag alternates between values on each call.</p>

<h2>Basic Switch (Two Values)</h2>
<pre>{open}switch 'odd', 'even'{close}</pre>
<p>Called 6 times:</p>
<ul>
  <li>{switch 'odd', 'even'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'odd', 'even'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'odd', 'even'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'odd', 'even'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'odd', 'even'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'odd', 'even'}</li>
</ul>

<h2>Switch for Alternating Row Colors</h2>
<pre>&lt;tr style="background:{open}switch '#f0f0f0', '#e0e0e0'{close}"&gt;</pre>
<table border="1">
  <tr style="background:{switch '#f0f0f0', '#e0e0e0'}"><td>Row 1</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:{switch '#f0f0f0', '#e0e0e0'}"><td>Row 2</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:{switch '#f0f0f0', '#e0e0e0'}"><td>Row 3</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:{switch '#f0f0f0', '#e0e0e0'}"><td>Row 4</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Switch with Multiple Values</h2>
<pre>{open}switch 'A', 'B', 'C'{close}</pre>
<p>Cycles through A, B, C:</p>
<ul>
  <li>{switch 'A', 'B', 'C'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'A', 'B', 'C'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'A', 'B', 'C'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'A', 'B', 'C'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'A', 'B', 'C'}</li>
  <li>{switch 'A', 'B', 'C'}</li>
</ul>
